description: Visually inspect all cable connections between each module to confirm that they are correctly and securely attached, with particular attention to possible miswiring or swapped polarities due to the cables being identical and unmarked., outcome='All cable connections between modules were visually inspected, and all are securely attached. No polarity inversions were detected throughout the chain from PSU to Load Cube. All positive and negative labeled cables are connected to their respective positive and negative counterparts.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=460.0, cost_breakdown=[('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_connections', 10.0), ('inspect_